    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8055-bc2a-ec5a9cc410de",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors analyzed how those processese were activated when engaging with the 4 learning tactics. Analysis between learning strategies shows signifcant differences on the 5 micro-processes, showing that trace data has the potential to highlight different types of behaviors. ",
